\begin_layout Enumerate

\emph on
Credits: 3p.

\emph default
 Consider the model 
\begin_inset Formula $y_{i}|\theta\stackrel{iid}{\sim}\text{Poisson}\left(\theta\right),$
\end_inset

 where 
\begin_inset Formula $f\left(y_{i}|\theta\right)=\frac{\theta^{y_{i}}e^{-\theta}}{y_{i}!}$
\end_inset

, for all observations.
 Use the following conjugate gamma prior for 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta$
\end_inset

 with parameters 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha=40$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta=2$
\end_inset

: 
\begin_inset Formula $p\left(\theta\right)\propto\theta^{\alpha-1}e^{-2\theta}$
\end_inset

.
